38 automobile club, premium financing company, health maintenance
39 organization, insurance holding company, mortgage guaranty insurance
40 company, risk retention or purchasing group, prepaid legal and dental
41 service plan, captive insurance company, automobile self-insurer or
42 reinsurance intermediary and any other legal entity under the jurisdiction
43 of the commissioner. The term "person" does not include insurance agents

